{"tid":1962400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正視聽。前線手足先係condom","createTime":"2020-04-07T12:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T12:44:54.000Z","uid":79793,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b356979d0a9cb2351a6eaf5997e337c84263aef2","tid":1962400,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"唔好再話咩狗先係condom<br />\n前線手足先係比人用完即棄嘅condom<br />\n班撚樣只會想無成本抗爭<br />\n<br />\n你若放棄誰佑我城<br />\n沒有從天而降的英雄<br />\n<br />\n呢啲浪漫嘅句子呃左幾多後生仔出黎<br />\n前線好型，好似英雄咁<br />\n我都覺啊，當初成班和理非圍住勇武拍手幾撚型<br />\n<br />\n一個月<br />\n兩個月<br />\n半年<br />\n拍手嘅繼續拍手，ig抗爭嘅繼續ig抗爭<br />\n<br />\n直至比人拉個一日，佢地仲係到好嬲<br />\n佢地唔係冇能力幫你，佢地只係唔想付出<br />\n<br />\n之後就用 日本社運 不分化 不割 唔好鬥黃做擋箭牌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武一個一個少，你覺得係比人拉哂？係死哂？灰哂啦，你地害到咁咖（同路人）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJokVMt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJokVMt.jpg&h=3ff27e56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人從未犯過法亦不鼓吹犯法行為，阿蛇唔洗跟我，我Ig抗爭做隻豬算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持警察 支持中國"},{"pid":"a3c866f011b79b98d9558fe45bd8bb5ee08c7bb1","tid":1962400,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:36:17.000Z","msg":"手足係condom"},{"pid":"71201868e7691f25d390b64e0819ee7a0b8ceb6c","tid":1962400,"uid":17799,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:38:11.000Z","msg":"入晒監倉做監躉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58972ba47edce85531e8c6cdbfbead6d5eef7da2","tid":1962400,"uid":4750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a980738b8688e2f10012d4d0b53222bcd2ae0864","tid":1962400,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71201868e7691f25d390b64e0819ee7a0b8ceb6c","tid":1962400,"uid":17799,"like":2,"dislike":1,"scor